TopicTitle: Ahhh, I remember my first successful mun landing and return, way back in 0.13.3

Articles.Content: Also, I almost forgot to mention that it was yesterday. That's right. Using NovaPunch remix and KSP 0.13.3, I successfully munshot and RETURNED! I've been to the Mun plenty of times before, but something went wrong EVERY SINGLE TIME I RETURNED! One time, I didn't have enough fuel. Many a time, I timewarped too fast, sometimes I had a staging mishap. But I JUST SUCCESSFULLY MUNSHOT, THEN KERBIN-I mean 'Kearth' -SHOT!
The only thing I manged to do was run out of fuel 100m above the muns surface. had to RCS to a point, ran out of rcs, and had to hardware break on the surface. only time I ever landed on mun in 13.3

Pics or it didn't happen

DAMN! I forgot that KSP 0.13.3 had screenshot capabilities!
